            <title>[LU-6315] sanity test_300g: stripe count 2 != 1 for /mnt/lustre/d300g.sanity/normal_dir/test1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6315</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f0fa0daa-c065-11e4-8be6-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f0fa0daa-c065-11e4-8be6-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_300g failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;stripe count 2 != 1 for /mnt/lustre/d300g.sanity/normal_dir/test1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this may related with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5118&quot; title=&quot;Failure on test suite sanity test_300g: expect 2 get 1 for /mnt/lustre/d300g.sanity/striped_dir/test2 &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5118&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5118&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 300g: check default striped directory for normal directory == 14:32:26 (1425133946)
checking normal_dir 2 1
checking normal_dir 1 0
checking normal_dir 2 1
checking normal_dir 2 -1
 sanity test_300g: @@@@@@ FAIL: stripe count 2 != 1 for /mnt/lustre/d300g.sanity/normal_dir/test1 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
